  "text": "Primary mouse RPE cells were isolated from 12-day-old Shaker1 mice and cultured on 24-well Transwell polycarbonate membrane inserts (Fisher Scientific), as described previously [CITATION_1] . The primary RPE cells were infected 48 hours later with either rAAV2/5-CMV-MYO7A or rAAV2/5-CMV-EGFP (10 4 GC/cell) as described above. Infected RPE cells were maintained in culture until MYO7A expression was assayed by Western blot at either 7 or 17 days after infection.",
